{"tid":465998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殘忍！深圳漢當街烤活鼠　女童蹲地淡定旁觀","createTime":"2017-11-12T06:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T06:46:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"44f358e53bda1602a2bcb6e3976f8e2194ca46a2","tid":465998,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/144614_b0708686b962ac40896f0791b5a89f7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F144614_b0708686b962ac40896f0791b5a89f7b.jpg&h=1f51f0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網傳深圳東門一名父親跟女兒在當街活烤老鼠的片段，片中可見一名中年男子左手不斷將用紙張生火，右手拿着放有老鼠的老鼠籠不斷在火上來回郁動，圖將籠內老鼠活活烤熟；現場另有一名女童蹲地靜靜在看着活烤老鼠的過程。 <br />\n<br />\n「太殘忍了吧？」、「老鼠擾人也不用活烤！」不少網民直斥片中男子殘忍離譜，「大教壞小！怎可在小孩面前做出這行為。」另有人批評：「冷血對待動物的態度『一代傳一代』，缺少教育是主因！」 <br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171111/mobile/bkncn-20171111120721920-1111_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171111%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171111120721920-1111_05011_001.html&d=m0e3U0I%2B%2Bcs63X%2BT%2FLg42kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=b33d6ff7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171111/mobile/bkncn-20171111120721920-1111_05011_001.html</a>"}]}